---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`Privacy Policy | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Privacy Policy of The Master Encyclopedia of Dreams" />
		<style>
			body {
				font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
				background-color: var(--bg-color, #0B0618);
				color: #E2DCF5;
				margin: 0;
			}
			.hero {
				position: relative;
				text-align: center;
				padding: 6em 1em;
				background-color: var(--accent-dark, #5B21B6);
				background-image:
					radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.35) 0%, transparent 50%),
					radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(103, 232, 249, 0.20) 0%, transparent 50%);
				width: 100vw;
				margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%);
				margin-right: calc(-50vw + 50%);
				border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent, #A78BFA);
			}
			.hero h1 {
				font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
				font-size: 3em;
				font-weight: 500;
				margin-bottom: 0.2em;
				letter-spacing: 2px;
				color: #F5F1FE;
				text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.4);
			}

			.content-section {
				width: 75vw;
				max-width: 75vw;
				margin-top: 4em;
				margin-bottom: 4em;
				margin-left: calc(-37.5vw + 50%);
				margin-right: calc(-37.5vw + 50%);
				padding: 3em;
				background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
				backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
				-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
				border-radius: 16px;
				box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
				border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
				line-height: 1.8;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}
			.content-section h3 {
				font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
				font-size: 1.8em;
				font-weight: 600;
				color: var(--accent, #A78BFA);
				border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.2);
				padding-bottom: 10px;
				margin-top: 1.5em;
				margin-bottom: 0.8em;
			}
			.content-section p {
				font-size: 1.1em;
				color: #E2DCF5;
				margin-bottom: 1.5em;
			}

			.content-section a {
				color: var(--accent, #A78BFA);
				text-decoration: underline;
			}
			
			.image-container {
				text-align: center;
				margin: 4em 0;
			}
			.image-container img {
				max-width: 100%;
				border-radius: 8px;
				box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main style="padding-top:0;">
			<section class="hero">
				<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
			</section>

			<section class="content-section">
				<p>At Encyclopedia of Dreams (accessible from https://www.encyclopedia-of-dreams.com), one of our main priorities is the privacy of our visitors. This Privacy Policy document contains types of information that is collected and recorded by our website and how we use it.</p>

				<h3>Who we are?</h3>
				<p>Our website address is: https://www.encyclopedia-of-dreams.com.</p>

				<h3>Advertising &ndash; Google AdSense</h3>
				<p>We use Google AdSense to serve ads on our website. Google, as a third-party vendor, uses cookies to serve ads based on your visit to this and other websites. Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads to our users based on their visit to our site and/or other sites on the Internet.<br/>Users may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Ads Settings</a>. Alternatively, you can opt out of a third-party vendor's use of cookies for personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.aboutads.info" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">www.aboutads.info</a>.</p>

				<h3>Comments</h3>
				<p>When visitors leave comments on the site we collect the data shown in the comments form, and also the visitor's IP address and browser user agent string to help spam detection. An anonymized string created from your email address (hash) may be provided to the Gravatar service.</p>

				<h3>Cookies</h3>
				<p>If you leave a comment on our site you may opt-in to saving your name, email address and website in cookies. These are for your convenience so that you do not have to fill in your details again. These cookies will last for one year.</p>

				<h3>Embedded content from other websites</h3>
				<p>Articles on this site may include embedded content (e.g. videos, images, articles, etc.). Embedded content from other websites behaves in the exact same way as if the visitor has visited the other website. These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, and monitor your interaction.</p>

				<h3>Disclaimer</h3>
				<p>The information provided by Encyclopedia of Dreams is for general informational purposes only. All information on the site is provided in good faith, however we make no representation or warranty of any kind regarding the accuracy or completeness of any information on the site.</p>

				<h3>Contact Us</h3>
				<p>The information provided by Encyclopedia of Dreams is for general informational purposes only. All information on the site is provided in good faith, however we make no representation or warranty of any kind regarding the accuracy or completeness of any information on the site.</p>
				
				<p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 3em; font-style: italic;">Effective Date: March 19, 2026</p>

				<div class="image-container">
					<img src="/media-images/hero-bg.webp" alt="Dream Mystery" onerror="this.style.display='none';"/>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>